node.text:
“Drive You Home" M/V BEHIND
.
Honestly a big thank you to TEAMWANG production my crew, on putting all this together, Thank you @mamesjao  clubmedia william 
Thank you @ryce_ent 
Annnndddd
Thank you to @_anthonylee_  and @v1nh  for guiding and always giving me inspirations in every way and of course we have @sinostage 
Always a fam

Everyone worked hard and went fulllll OUT on this
Im blessed to have all of you
And no matter what, its definitely a stamp / a decent chapter in our journey.
.

#DriveYouHome
#jacksonwang
#TEAMWANG
#KNOWMEvlog
#잭슨 
#王嘉爾
@teamwang
